
  Palossand    Ghost Type Pokémon

  Possessed people controlled 
  by this Pokémon transformed its 
  sand mound into a castle.  As 
  it evolved, its power to curse 
  grew ever stronger. 
	Evolution Chain
      Sandygast ► Palossand

